libcmime
------------------------------------------
libcmime is a lightweight mime library, written in C. It attempts to be a
general library for parsing and creating mime email messages and is designed to
provide an easy to use and easy to integrate interface for developers. libcmime
is a pretty fresh project so the library is still in beta state and there will
be early and frequent releases.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libcmime-devel-0.2.2-1bl1
  libcmime0.2-0.2.2-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  bison-3.8.2-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  flex-2.6.4-2
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://www.libcmime.org/

Canonical download:
  https://www.libcmime.org/files/libcmime-0.2.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcmime-0.2.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcmime-0.2.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcmime-0.2.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcmime-0.2.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcmime0.2-0.2.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcmime-devel-0.2.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcmime)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcmime.README
  /usr/share/doc/libcmime/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libcmime/CHANGELOG
  /usr/share/doc/libcmime/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libcmime/README

(libcmime0.2)
  /usr/bin/cygcmime-0.2.dll

(libcmime-devel)
  /usr/include/cmime.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_address.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_base64.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_config.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_header.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_list.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_message.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_part.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_qp.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_string.h
  /usr/include/cmime/cmime_util.h
  /usr/lib/libcmime.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libcmime.pc

